This directory contains Ed25519 signature-edge test vectors derived from:

  ed25519-speccheck
  https://github.com/novifinancial/ed25519-speccheck
  Upstream commit: 65519336fda78a3d016e947df6d82848aca0c9da
  Copyright (c) Facebook, Inc. and its affiliates.
