The 12 edge vectors (speccheck-0 through speccheck-11 in vectors.json) are the
test cases from that project, which accompanies:

  Konstantinos Chalkias, Francois Garillot, and Valeria Nikolaenko.
  "Taming the Many EdDSAs." Security Standardisation Research (SSR) 2020.

A full copy of the Apache License, Version 2.0 is included alongside this
NOTICE in this directory:

  LICENSE-APACHE-2.0

(also available at http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0).

The remaining vectors are not from ed25519-speccheck:
  - rfc8032-vector-1 is from RFC 8032 Section 7.1, Test 1.
  - peac-sign-positive is generated by the PEAC signer from a fixed seed.

The per-vector "empirical" and "peac_expected" fields are computed by PEAC and
are not part of the upstream ed25519-speccheck data.
